ce","last_activity_date":1385941956,"creation_date":1362517300,"answer_count":1,"title":"Number of reading frames in nucleotide sequence","body":"<p>In class of molecular biology was posed this question:<\/p>\n\n<p>\"How many reading frames start in sequence of nucleotides 5' ... ATATGAATGATGACAT... 3' ?\"<\/p>\n","question_id":7453,"tags":["homework","dna-sequencing"],"score":1,"accepted_answer_id":7456,"down_vote_count":1,"is_answered":true,"view_count":1336,"up_vote_count":2,"last_edit_date":1362519685},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/a2beb162438985ede0a49b240aa17ca1?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":985,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/985/lance-pollard","reputation":144,"display_name":"Lance Pollard"},"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/WzDd8.jpg?s=128&g=1","user_type":"moderator","user_id":374,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/374/adam-lear","reputation":101,"display_name":"Adam Lear"},"score":2,"post_id":2529,"edited":false,"creation_date":1339098893,"comment_id":3506,"body":"If you already found some sites that fit the bill, they may be better off posted as an answer. Per the <a href=\"http://biology.stackexchange.com/faq#dontask\">FAQ<\/a>: <code>avoid asking subjective questions where... your answer is provided along with the question, and you expect more answers: &quot;I use ______ for ______, what do you use?&quot;<\/code>."},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/ef067cf09ffd3cc8f069bacec73c8202?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":222,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/222/david-lebauer","reputation":780,"display_name":"David LeBauer","accept_rate":80},"score":1,"post_id":2529,"edited":false,"creation_date":1339121986,"comment_id":3512,"body":"What are you looking for that these sites lack?"},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/210cc4a4b2f281aaffe0b26521fe1ab8?s=128&d=id